title: Pink Floyd - Rainbow Show (Bootleg)
description:
Tracks 1-10 recorded at the Rainbow Theatre, London, UK on 20th February 1972.
Track 11 recorded at the Sheffield City Hall, UK on 22nd December 1970. One of only four(!) live performances of 'Alan'n Psychedelic Breakfast'.

1. Speak To Me
2. Breathe
3. On The Run
4. Time
5. The Great Gig In The Sky
6. Money
7. Us And Them
8. Any Colour You Like
9. Brain Damage
10. Eclipse

11. Alan's Psychedelic Breakfast
